A beggar identified as Hadiza Ibrahim surprised everyone after she was arrested in Abuja with over N500k and $100.
The incident have thrown many into confusion as some people at the scene were linking the woman to kidnappers. Others were on the view that she might be into child trafficking or rituals.
As of the time of this report, it could not authoritatively confirm where the woman is from or how she is in possession of such huge amount of money.
Although sources later confirmed that she has been handed over to the police for further investigation.






